'''Ngiap-lang''' (𥍉爧) he [[thai-hi]] ke [[thien-hò]] piong chhut-lòi ke chhṳ-yèn hien-siong, thûng-sòng he [[phau-fûng-yí]] ke sṳ̀-heu khon to, ya voi chhai [[fó-sân]] pau-fap fe̍t-chá [[sâ-chhṳ̀n fûng-phau]] ke sṳ̀-heu chhut-hien. Thai-hi piong thien voi tông kô vûn, lo̍k to thi sông cho-tet chiông [[sâ]], [[sa̍k]] pien-sṳ̀n [[pô-lì]], thiên-khûng ya voi ngie̍t to yû sám-kông.

Yit-pân hàng-lùi ke sṳ̀-heu voi siên khon to ngiap-lang, chai thâng to [[lùi-kûng]].

